The paper deals with detecting actions in videos, which is a task related to computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method involves deep learning techniques, specifically end-to-end training with joint loss, which falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The experiments are conducted on a standard dataset, which is related to multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR).
